            <thetext>Currently, assigning a text color to an text field will also assign the text color to its placeholder element. This is misleading because after the color has set once, you can not distinguish if a text or a placeholder is shown. We should just remove the apply of the color and keep the placeholder always in the initial color. This would also align with the native implementation of the placeholder e.g. in chrome.</thetext>
